'''朱利安·保羅·阿桑奇'''（{{lang-en|Julian Paul Assange}}，發音：{{IPA|/əˈsɑːnʒ/}}，{{bd|1971年|7月3日|catIdx=Assange}}），[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]][[記者|記者]]，揭密網站[[維基解密|維基解密]]董事、发言人。[[維基解密|維基解密]]在2010年發布了一系列由[[美國陸軍|美國陸軍]][[情報分析|情報分析]]員[[切爾西·曼寧|切爾西·曼寧]]（Chelsea Manning，布拉德利·曼寧，Bradley Manning）提供解密事件，引起國際關注。自創辦至今，維基解密公佈了相當數量機密文件，這之中包括關於美國部隊[[附帶謀殺|巴格達空襲附帶謀殺]]視頻（2010年4月）<ref name="ReferenceA">{{YouTube|5rXPrfnU3G0|''Collateral Murder''}}, 5 April 2000. Retrieved 28 March 2014.</ref><ref name=beeb150313>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-19426382 |title=Q&A: Julian Assange and the law |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=2015-03-13 |access-date=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2022-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220622151306/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-19426382 }}</ref>、[[阿富汗戰爭_(2001年－2021年)|阿富汗戰爭]]的行徑、發生在[[肯尼亞|肯尼亞]][[私刑|法外處決]]、[[维基解密泄露美国外交电报事件|美國外交電報事件]]（2010年11月）、在[[象牙海岸|象牙海岸]]有毒废物傾倒事件文件，[[山达基|山达基]]手冊等。<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web | url = http://www.smh.com.au/opinion/politics/leaks-pour-forth-from-the-wiki-well-of-information-20100408-ruxn.html | title = WikiLeak And Apache Attack In Iraq—Julian Assange | publisher = [[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]] | date = 2010-04-09 | accessdate = 2010-12-03 | archive-date = 2011-08-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110830231218/http://www.smh.com.au/opinion/politics/leaks-pour-forth-from-the-wiki-well-of-information-20100408-ruxn.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>2010年11月28日起，維基解密與其他媒體夥伴開始發佈秘密的[[维基解密泄露美国外交电报事件|美國外交電報事件]]。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/blog/2010/dec/03/wikileaks-julian-assange-online | title = WikiLeaks cables: Live Q&A with Julian Assange | publisher = The Guardian | date = 2010-12-03 | accessdate = 2010-12-03 | archive-date = 2020-12-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201218150722/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/blog/2010/dec/03/wikileaks-julian-assange-online | dead-url = no }}</ref>2010年洩密事件後，[[美國聯邦政府|美國政府]]對[[維基解密|維基解密]]展開刑事調查<ref name="Holder says">{{cite news |last1=Yost |first1=Pete |title=Holder says WikiLeaks under criminal investigation |url=http://archive.boston.com/news/nation/washington/articles/2010/11/29/ag_says_government_is_active_in_scrutinizing_leaks/ |access-date=2019-07-27 |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |work=Boston Globe |date=2010-11-29 |archive-date=2022-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220621063241/http://archive.boston.com/news/nation/washington/articles/2010/11/29/ag_says_government_is_active_in_scrutinizing_leaks/ }}</ref>。

2010年11月30日，在位於瑞典的國際公共檢察官辦公室要求之下，[[國際刑警組織|國際刑警組織]]以涉嫌性犯罪為由，對阿桑奇發出國際逮捕令。<ref name="interpol"/>12月7日，阿桑奇向[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]投案，<ref name="bbc1207">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-11937110 | title = Wikileaks founder Julian Assange arrested in London | publisher = BBC | date = 2010-12-07 | accessdate = 2010-12-07 | archive-date = 2020-12-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201207061843/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-11937110 | dead-url = no }}</ref>但他否認相關指控。<ref name="guard0712">{{cite news| url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2010/dec/07/julian-assange-refused-bail-over-rape-allegations| title = Julian Assange refused bail over rape allegations| author = Paul Owen, Caroline Davies, Sam Jones and agencies| publisher = The Guardian| date = 2010-12-07| accessdate = 2010-12-07| archive-date = 2012-03-08| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120308172157/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2010/dec/07/julian-assange-refused-bail-over-rape-allegations| dead-url = no}}</ref>2012年6月19日，阿桑奇在[[保釋|保釋]]期間進入{{Link-en|厄瓜多駐英國大使館|Embassy of Ecuador, London}}尋求[[政治庇護|政治庇護]]，同年8月，阿桑奇獲厄瓜多爾政府政治庇護，之後在大使館居住近七年。

與維基解密相關的工作使阿桑奇榮獲多項榮譽，例如2009年的“國際特赦傳媒獎”與2008年《[[經濟學人|經濟學人]]》“言論自由獎”。同時，阿桑奇的工作亦備受批評，例如美國[[白宮|白宮]]稱他的行為是“魯莽和危險的”。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.haaretz.com/news/international/russia-official-wikileaks-founder-should-get-nobel-prize-1.329555 | title = Russia official: WikiLeaks founder should get Nobel Prize | publisher = Haaretz | date = 2010-12-08 | accessdate = 2010-12-14 | archive-date = 2010-12-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101210162810/http://www.haaretz.com/news/international/russia-official-wikileaks-founder-should-get-nobel-prize-1.329555 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

成為维基解密的代言人與編輯之前，阿桑奇曾是[[物理|物理]]、[[數學|數學]]系[[學生|學生]]、[[程式設計師|程式設計師]]、[[駭客|駭客]]。<ref>[[明報|明報]]專訊，[http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/100822/4/jtt8.html 〈維基解密創辦人「墮美人計」女子現身指遭受性暴力〉] {{Wayback|url=http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/100822/4/jtt8.html |date=20100826100935 }}，《明報》2010年8月23日</ref>他曾辗转多個國家，居无定所，偶爾也在公共場合露面，就[[新聞自由|新聞自由]]、審查制度與調查性新聞工作闡述自己的看法。

2019年4月4日，维基解密在推特上发布了一条来自厄瓜多尔政府高层人士的消息称，阿桑奇将被以丑闻为借口驱逐，并且与英国达成了逮捕他的协议。<ref>{{Cite web|title=维基解密在推特发布阿桑奇可能被英国逮捕的消息|url=https://twitter.com/wikileaks/status/1113919962995884033|work=@wikileaks|date=2019-04-04|accessdate=2019-04-11|language=en|last=WikiLeaks|author=|publisher=|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120094126/https://twitter.com/wikileaks/status/1113919962995884033|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年4月11日，伦敦警察廳称獲厄瓜多尔驻英國大使馆館員批准，入館拘捕朱利安·阿桑奇。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2019/04/11/uk/julian-assange-arrested-gbr-intl/index.html |title=Julian Assange has been arrested |website=CNN |date=2019-04-11 |accessdate=2019-04-11 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105020314/https://edition.cnn.com/2019/04/11/uk/julian-assange-arrested-gbr-intl/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

自2019年4月以來，阿桑奇一直被關押在倫敦的最高保安级别{{le|貝爾馬什監獄|HM Prison Belmarsh}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Wikileaks founder Julian Assange is planning to get married inside top-security Belmarsh prison |url=https://www.standard.co.uk/news/uk/wikileaks-julian-assange-marriage-belmarsh-prison-b942937.html |website=Evening Standard |access-date=2021-08-31 |archive-date=2022-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220623025206/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/uk/wikileaks-julian-assange-marriage-belmarsh-prison-b942937.html }}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
=== 成长经历 ===
阿桑奇出生在澳大利亞[[昆士蘭州|昆士蘭州]]東北海岸的[[湯斯維爾|湯斯維爾]]，童年主要在鄰近的[[磁島|磁島]]上度過。在他未出生前，母親克莉斯汀與阿桑奇生父John Shipton離異。阿桑奇一歲時，母親克莉斯汀與劇導演布萊特·阿桑奇結婚。小阿桑奇的姓也是從繼父得來。<ref name="interpol">{{Cite news | url = http://www.interpol.int/public/data/wanted/notices/data/2010/86/2010_52486.asp | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101204083534/http://www.interpol.int/public/data/wanted/notices/data/2010/86/2010_52486.asp | archivedate = 2010-12-07 | title = ASSANGE, Julian Paul | date = 2010-11-30 | publisher = Interpol | postscript = . | access-date = 2010-12-07 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="khatchadourian" /><ref name="7news/CNN">{{cite news | title =The secret life of Julian Assange | url =http://www.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/asiapcf/12/09/assange.profile/ | publisher =[[CNN|CNN]] | date =2010-12-02 | accessdate =2010-12-02 | archive-date =2013-06-17 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130617005412/http://www.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/asiapcf/12/09/assange.profile/ | dead-url =no }}</ref>母親與繼父運營一家巡迴劇團，總是四處奔波。阿桑奇的繼父在描述阿桑奇時，稱他是一個“非常有洞察力的孩子”，“對是非黑白有個人的見解”，而且“總是為弱者撐腰，很反感聯合起來（欺負他人）的人”。<ref name="7news/CNN"/>

1979年，阿桑奇的母親與繼父離異，母親後來與Leif Meynell，又名Leif Hamilton的男人變得關係緊密，而他則是[[澳洲|澳洲]]新興宗教「{{link-en|The Family (Australian New Age group)|The Family (Australian New Age group)|The Family}}」的一名成員。兩人生下一名兒子，後來這對情侶在1982年分手，並與阿桑奇的第二位繼父在兩人的兒子阿桑奇同母異父弟弟的撫養權上產生糾紛。阿桑奇的母親帶著阿桑奇與他的弟弟開始了長達五年的逃離生活。在阿桑奇14歲時，他就已搬了無數次家。他所就讀的學校不計其數，接受的教育斷斷續續，經常在家自學，<ref name="khatchadourian">{{cite news | title = No Secrets: Julian Assange's Mission for Total Transparency | url = http://www.newyorker.com/reporting/2010/06/07/100607fa_fact_khatchadourian?currentPage=all | first = Raffi | last = Khatchadourian | newspaper = [[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]] | date = 2010-06-07 | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archive-date = 2012-09-04 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20120904/http://www.newyorker.com/reporting/2010/06/07/100607fa_fact_khatchadourian?currentPage=all | dead-url = no }}</ref>也參加函授班以及非正式地跟隨一些大學教授學習。<ref name="Raffi">{{cite journal|author=Raffi Khatchadourian|title=No Secrets|journal=New Yorker|date=2010-06-07|url=http://www.newyorker.com/reporting/2010/06/07/100607fa_fact_khatchadourian|accessdate=2010-11-05|archive-date=2010-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100722005314/http://www.newyorker.com/reporting/2010/06/07/100607fa_fact_khatchadourian|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 黑客攻擊 ===
1987年，16歲的阿桑奇在網絡上以''Mendax''之名成為一個駭客，<ref name=Raffi />他與另外兩名駭客一起組建了一個叫做「萬國顛覆」（International Subversives）的團體，以侵入其他機構的電腦為樂趣。他的黑客名''Mendax''取自古羅馬詩人[[賀拉斯|賀拉斯]]的名言「splendide mendax」，意為“高貴的虛偽”。他在與作家{{tsl|en|Suelette Dreyfus|賽利特·德累福斯}}合著的《地下》（''Underground''）一書中，描述了他心目中的駭客法則：「不要損壞（包括崩潰）你所侵入的電腦系統；不要更改那些系統中的信息（除了修改日誌掩蓋自己的蹤跡）；分享所獲得的信息。」<ref name=Raffi />

1991年，由於阿桑奇侵入其他電腦，[[澳洲警方|澳洲警方]]搜查了他在[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]的住所。<ref name="theaustralian">{{cite news | title = Rudd Government blacklist hacker monitors police | url = http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/rudd-government-blacklist-hacker-monitors-police/story-e6frg8yx-1225718288350 | first = Richard | last = Guilliatt | newspaper = [[The_Australian|The Australian]] | date = 2009-05-30 | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archive-date = 2012-05-27 | archive-url = https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20120527015312/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/national-affairs/defence/rudd-government-blacklist-hacker-monitors-police/story-e6frg8yx-1225718288350 | dead-url = no }} [lead-in to a longer article in that day's ''The Weekend Australian Magazine'']</ref>警方發現，阿桑奇利用調製解調器，<ref name="aolnews">{{cite news | first = Sharon | last = Weinberger | title = Who Is Behind WikiLeaks? | url = http://www.aolnews.com/nation/article/besides-julian-assange-who-is-behind-WikiLeaks/19430055 | date = 2010-04-07 | newspaper = [[AOL|AOL]] | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archive-date = 2019-03-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190315233940/http://www.aolnews.com/nation/article/besides-julian-assange-who-is-behind-WikiLeaks/19430055 | dead-url = no }}</ref>曾侵入一家澳洲大學與加拿大[[北電網絡|北電網絡]]<ref name="khatchadourian" />的電腦系統。1992年，阿桑奇對24項與侵入電腦系統有關的指控認罪。因為表現良好，在被罰款2100澳元后，阿桑奇被保釋釋放。<ref name="khatchadourian" /><ref name="smh1">{{cite news | first = Bernard | last = Lagan | title = International man of mystery | url = http://www.smh.com.au/technology/technology-news/international-man-of-mystery-20100409-ryvf.html | date = 2010-04-10 | newspaper = The Sydney Morning Herald | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archive-date = 2016-01-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160130094618/http://www.smh.com.au/technology/technology-news/international-man-of-mystery-20100409-ryvf.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>公訴人稱，“調查顯示，此宗案件，系由當事人對情報信息的好奇及對於侵入其他電腦樂趣的追求所引起，並無其他因素”。<ref name="khatchadourian" />當時這一新聞曾被澳洲電視臺的新聞節目報導。<ref>澳洲SBS台，Dateline節目對阿桑奇的專題報導</ref>

建立維基解密后，阿桑奇曾提到：“（媒體總是提及我之前的黑客經歷）實在是有些惱人。就因為我以前（就黑客經歷）與別人出了本書，也有相關的紀錄片，人們就對此津津樂道，媒體也用盡了複製粘貼的伎倆。人們都忘了，那個已經是二十年前的事了。在現在還能看到有文章中稱我為電腦黑客，著實讓我十分惱怒。不是因為我認為那是我不光彩的歷史；不，我對於那段經歷感到驕傲。只是因為我現在是維基解密的發言人，媒體就翻出以前的舊賬。我想，這背後的動機與試圖給出的暗示，想必很明確。”<ref name="Forbes">{{cite web | last = Greenberg | first = Andy | url = http://blogs.forbes.com/andygreenberg/2010/11/29/an-interview-with-wikileaks-julian-assange/6/ | title = An Interview With WikiLeaks’ Julian Assange—Andy Greenberg – The Firewall | publisher = Blogs.forbes.com | date =  | accessdate = 2010-12-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101211165856/http://blogs.forbes.com/andygreenberg/2010/11/29/an-interview-with-wikileaks-julian-assange/6/ | archive-date = 2010-12-11 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

=== 監護權問題 ===
18歲時，阿桑奇與一名女子同居並生了一個孩子——丹尼爾。<ref name="crikey" />該女子在阿桑奇住所被警方搜查后帶著兒子離開了他。直到1999年，他才與該名女子達成監護協議。丹尼爾有理學學位，於一家軟件設計公司工作。<ref name="crikey" />在父親問他是否願意加入維基解密工作團隊時，他沒有接受，因為他不覺得維基解密會有很大成就。<ref>[http://www.crikey.com.au/2010/09/17/daniel-assange-i-never-thought-wikileaks-would-succeed/ Daniel Assange: I never thought WikiLeaks would succeed] {{Wayback|url=http://www.crikey.com.au/2010/09/17/daniel-assange-i-never-thought-wikileaks-would-succeed/ |date=20101208211859 }}, Nick Johns-Wickberg, 17 September 2010, [[Crikey|Crikey]]</ref>在丹尼爾的眼中，父親是個十分聰慧的人，并有著與此相關的一系列、特徵性的煩惱和憂慮。<ref name="crikey" />例如，父親不願意與理解能力無法與他自己保持在同一水平的人共事，因為會讓他自己感到懊喪。<ref name="crikey" />而且父親對於政治活動總是很感興趣，也熱愛科學、哲學與對知識的普遍追求，他認為地球上的每個人都應當有機會獲得這類知識。<ref name="crikey" />作為父親，阿桑奇對於與自己的兒子分享自己的知識抱有很高的熱情，而這也是丹尼爾最喜歡父親的地方。<ref name="crikey" />2010年阿桑奇陷入性侵犯困境后，丹尼爾曾在[[臉書|臉書]]上留言“那個人（即自己父親）頗擅長於與女性為敵”（''That man does have a way of making a lot of female enemies''），后被《紐約郵報》作為材料，推出「我的維基父親在與女人相處方面簡直糟透了」（''My Wiki dad's just awful with the ladies''）一文。<ref>[http://www.nypost.com/p/news/international/my_wiki_dad_just_awful_with_the_lPuc6BTUKeNNMwZLeUTFJK My Wiki dad's just awful with the ladies] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nypost.com/p/news/international/my_wiki_dad_just_awful_with_the_lPuc6BTUKeNNMwZLeUTFJK |date=20121107105932 }}，2010年8月27日，紐約郵報．</ref>丹尼爾否認《紐約郵報》曾對其作出採訪，也覺得從原話得出後者的結論，“的確扯得有點遠”。<ref name="crikey" />

== 編程和學術 ==
1993年，阿桑奇參與建立“薩伯比亞公共接入网络”（''Suburbia Public Access Network''）——澳洲最早的互聯網服務提供商之一。<ref name="Forbes">{{cite web | last = Greenberg | first = Andy | url = http://blogs.forbes.com/andygreenberg/2010/11/29/an-interview-with-wikileaks-julian-assange/6/ | title = An Interview With WikiLeaks’ Julian Assange—Andy Greenberg – The Firewall | publisher = Blogs.forbes.com | date =  | accessdate = 2010-12-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101211165856/http://blogs.forbes.com/andygreenberg/2010/11/29/an-interview-with-wikileaks-julian-assange/6/ | archive-date = 2010-12-11 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://suburbia.org.au | title = Suburbia Public Access Network | publisher = Suburbia.org.au | date =  | accessdate = 2010-12-04 | archive-date = 2014-12-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141218182014/http://suburbia.org.au/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>1994年起，居於墨爾本的阿桑奇成為程序設計員，開始自由軟件的研發。<ref name="smh1" />1995年，阿桑奇寫成“Strobe”，即首個自由開源的端口掃描器。<ref name="seclists">Assange stated, "In this limited application strobe is said to be faster and more flexible than ISS2.1（an expensive, but verbose security checker by Christopher Klaus）or PingWare（also commercial, and even more expensive）." See [http://seclists.org/bugtraq/1995/Mar/65 Strobe v1.01: Super Optimised TCP port surveyor] {{Wayback|url=http://seclists.org/bugtraq/1995/Mar/65 |date=20210211210131 }}</ref><ref name="strobe">{{cite web | title = strobe-1.06: A super optimised TCP port surveyor | url = http://hpux.connect.org.uk/hppd/hpux/Networking/Admin/strobe-1.06 | publisher = The Porting And Archive Centre for HP-UX | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archive-date = 2021-02-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210211213703/http://hpux.connect.org.uk/hppd/hpux/Networking/Admin/strobe-1.06/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>1996年，他為[[PostgreSQL|PostgreSQL]]計劃提供多個補丁。<ref name="pgsql">{{cite web | url = http://www.postgresql.org/community/contributors | title = PostgreSQL contributors | publisher = Postgresql.org | date =  | accessdate = 2010-11-29 | archive-date = 2021-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210306051828/https://www.postgresql.org/community/contributors/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>1997年，阿桑奇與他人合著《地下：駭客與瘋狂的傳奇及對電子前沿的癡迷》（''Underground: Tales of Hacking, Madness and Obsession on the Electronic Frontier''），書中提到自己的黑客經歷。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wired.co.uk/magazine/archive/2009/10/start/exposed-wikileaks-secrets?page=all|title=Exposed: Wikileaks' secrets|author=Annabel Symington|publisher=Wired Magazine|date=2009-09-01|accessdate=2010-12-07|archive-date=2015-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914225127/http://www.wired.co.uk/magazine/archive/2009/10/start/exposed-wikileaks-secrets?page=all|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="suelette">{{Cite book | title = [[Underground_(Suelette_Dreyfus_book)|Underground: Tales of Hacking, Madness and Obsession on the Electronic Frontier]] | first = Suelette | last = Dreyfus | year = 1997 | isbn = 1-86330-595-5}}</ref>1997年起，他與別人共同研究出''Rubberhose''否認加密系統。這一系統后成為[[Linux|Linux]]一個軟件包的基礎，為[[软磨硬泡攻击|软磨硬泡攻击]]（''rubber-hose cryptanalysis''）提供[[似是而非的否认|似是而非的否认]]（''plausible deniability''）。<ref name="singel">{{cite news | first = Ryan | last = Singel | title = Immune to Critics, Secret-Spilling Wikileaks Plans to Save Journalism ... and the World | url = http://www.wired.com/politics/onlinerights/news/2008/07/wikileaks?currentPage=all | date = 2008-07-03 | newspaper = [[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archive-date = 2013-09-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130909054954/http://www.wired.com/politics/onlinerights/news/2008/07/wikileaks?currentPage=all | dead-url = no }}</ref>他發明該系統的初衷是為人權工作者提供保護敏感數據的工具。<ref name="rubberhose">{{cite web | first = Suelette | last = Dreyfus | title = The Idiot Savants' Guide to Rubberhose | url = http://iq.org/~proff/rubberhose.org/current/src/doc/maruguide/t1.html | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archive-date = 2010-08-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100813032734/http://iq.org/~proff/rubberhose.org/current/src/doc/maruguide/t1.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>除此以外，他參與發明的自由軟件還有：[[Usenet|Usenet]]緩存軟件NNTPCache<ref name="nntpcache">{{cite web | title=NNTPCache: Authors | url=http://iq.org/~proff/nntpcache.org | accessdate=2010-06-16 | archive-date=2010-11-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101123054222/http://iq.org/~proff/nntpcache.org/ | dead-url=yes }}</ref>與為網絡搜索引擎設計的命令行界面Surfraw。

阿桑奇據稱曾在不同時段在六家大學就讀。<ref name="pdf">{{cite web | title = PdF Conference 2010: Speakers | url = http://personaldemocracy.com/pdf-conference-2010-june-3-5-new-york-city-speakers#assange | publisher = [[Personal_Democracy_Forum|Personal Democracy Forum]] | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archive-date = 2012-05-27 | archive-url = https://archive.today/20120527042208/http://personaldemocracy.com/pdf-conference-2010-june-3-5-new-york-city-speakers%23assange#assange | dead-url = no }}</ref>2003-2006年間，他在[[墨爾本大學|墨爾本大學]]學習物理與數學，但他從未畢業，在所學的多數數學課程中他也只勉強及格。<ref name="khatchadourian" /><ref>{{cite news | first=John | last=Rosenthal | coauthors= | script-title=en:Mythbusted: Professor says WikiLeaks founder was ‘no star’ mathematician | date=2010-12-12 | publisher= | url=http://dailycaller.com/2010/12/12/mythbusted-professor-says-wikileaks-founder-was-no-star-mathematician/ | work=[[The_Daily_Caller|The Daily Caller]] | pages= | accessdate=2010-12-12 | language= | archive-date=2020-07-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722073126/https://dailycaller.com/2010/12/12/mythbusted-professor-says-wikileaks-founder-was-no-star-mathematician/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>他也曾學習哲學與神經科學。<ref name="pdf" />他個人網頁上，還稱自己曾在2005年左右代表墨大參加[[澳洲全國物理競賽|澳洲全國物理競賽]]。<ref name="khatchadourian" /><ref name="cream">{{cite web | first = Julian | last = Assange | title = The cream of Australian Physics | publisher = IQ.ORG | date = 2006-07-12 | url = http://iq.org/#ThecreamofAustralianPhysics | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071020051936/http://iq.org/#ThecreamofAustralianPhysics | archivedate = 2007-10-20 | quote = A year before, also at ANU, I represented my university at the Australian National Physics Competition. At the prize ceremony, the head of ANU physics, motioned to us and said, 'You are the cream of Australian physics'. | access-date = 2007-10-20 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

阿桑奇於[[墨爾本大學|墨爾本大學]]學習物理，稱是為了智力刺激，試圖破解宇宙背後的秘密法則。但是他發現，即使是科學界，也是被因循守舊者把持。他認為人類的鬥爭是個體與機構之爭。他還起草了一份名為《陰謀即統治》的宣言，宣稱不合法的統治本質上就是陰謀，它是官員們「暗中合作、致力於損害國民」的產物。當一個政權內部的溝通渠道中斷後，同謀者之間的信息流動一定會萎縮，在這種情況下，當信息交流趨近與零的時候，陰謀就會終止。揭秘是信息戰的工具。<ref name=Raffi />

== 創立維基解密 ==
