阿桑奇稱維基解密所發佈的機密文件數量，超過世界上其他新聞媒體的加起來的總和。他說道：“我不是想說維基解密有多成功，而是想表示世界媒體危機重重的現狀。一個五個人的團隊公佈了比其他媒體加起來都多的機密文件，這是（媒體業的）恥辱。”<ref name="smh2" />他提倡新聞業應是“透明”與“细致嚴謹”的，因為用物理論文来打比方，“物理論文只有寫清楚實驗內容和結果，才可以發表出去，新聞業也應該採取類似的標準”。<ref name="journalism_2010">{{cite web | url = http://blogs.journalism.co.uk/editors/2010/07/12/a-real-free-press-for-the-first-time-in-history-wikileaks-editor-speaks-out-in-london | title = 'A real free press for the first time in history': WikiLeaks editor speaks out in London | publisher = Blogs.journalism.co.uk | date = 2010-07-12 | accessdate = 2010-08-21 | archive-date = 2011-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111006014714/http://blogs.journalism.co.uk/editors/2010/07/12/a-real-free-press-for-the-first-time-in-history-wikileaks-editor-speaks-out-in-london/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Military/2010/0726/Julian-Assange-the-hacker-who-created-WikiLeaks | title = Julian Assange: the hacker who created WikiLeaks | publisher = Csmonitor.com | date =  | accessdate = 2010-08-22 | archive-date = 2018-06-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612230353/https://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Military/2010/0726/Julian-Assange-the-hacker-who-created-WikiLeaks | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2006年，美國{{le|CounterPunch}}雜誌稱他是“澳洲最聲名狼藉的前電腦黑客”。<ref name="wankworm">Julian Assange: [http://www.counterpunch.org/assange11252006.html The Anti-Nuclear WANK Worm. The Curious Origins of Political Hacktivism] {{Wayback|url=http://www.counterpunch.org/assange11252006.html |date=20080419071903 }} {{le|CounterPunch}}, 25 November/ 26 2006</ref>澳洲《[[世紀報|世紀報]]》稱他是“世界上最迷人的人物之一”和“互聯網的自由鬥士”。<ref name="theage1">{{cite news | first = Nikki | last = Barrowclough | title = Keeper of secrets | url = http://www.theage.com.au/national/keeper-of-secrets-20100521-w230.html | newspaper = [[The_Age|The Age]] | date = 2010-05-22 | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archive-date = 2010-05-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100523153440/http://www.theage.com.au/national/keeper-of-secrets-20100521-w230.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>“[[個人民主論壇|個人民主論壇]]”稱青年時代的阿桑奇是“澳洲最有名的守德電腦駭客”。<ref name="pdf" />阿桑奇則稱自己“極其地憤世嫉俗”。<ref name="theage1" />

在2010年[[奧斯陸自由論壇|奧斯陸自由論壇]]上，阿桑奇對維基解密的創辦宗旨如此解釋：<ref>{{Cite web
