2019年4月2日，厄瓜多尔总统莫雷诺表示阿桑奇违反政治庇护条款，理由是网上出现莫雷诺牵涉腐败丑闻的照片证据<ref name="r040619">{{cite news |title=Ecuador's president says Assange breached terms of London embassy asylum |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ecuador-wikileaks-assange/ecuadors-president-says-assange-breached-terms-of-london-embassy-asylum-idUSKCN1RE1TL |access-date=2019-04-06 |work=[[路透社|Reuters]] |date=2019-04-06 |archive-date=2022-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220621165246/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ecuador-wikileaks-assange/ecuadors-president-says-assange-breached-terms-of-london-embassy-asylum-idUSKCN1RE1TL }}</ref><ref name="f040619">{{cite news |title=Ecuador president blames WikiLeaks for leak of private data |url=https://www.foxnews.com/world/ecuador-president-blames-wikileaks-for-leak-of-private-data |access-date=2019-04-06 |agency=[[美联社|Associated Press]] |publisher=Fox News Channel |date=2019-04-03 |archive-date=2022-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220623003908/https://www.foxnews.com/world/ecuador-president-blames-wikileaks-for-leak-of-private-data }}</ref>。维基解密表示没有发布有关照片，只是报道了厄瓜多尔立法机构对莫雷诺展开的腐败调查<ref name="f040619" />。维基解密援引厄瓜多尔政府内部的消息人士，称由于涉及争议，政府已就将阿桑奇驱逐出大使馆、转由英国警方拘留达成协议<ref name="orozco">{{cite news |last1=Orozco |first1=Jose |last2=Penny |first2=Thomas |last3=Biggs |first3=Stuart |title=Ecuador to Expel Assange Within 'Hours to Days,' WikiLeaks Says |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-04-05/ecuador-to-expel-assange-within-hours-to-days-wikileaks-says |access-date=2019-04-06 |publisher=Bloomberg L.P. |url-access=subscription |archive-date=2022-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220416154115/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-04-05/ecuador-to-expel-assange-within-hours-to-days-wikileaks-says }}</ref><ref name="grierson">{{cite news |last1=Grierson |first1=Jamie |title=Why is WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange in Ecuador's embassy? |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2019/apr/05/why-is-wikileaks-founder-julian-assange-in-london-ecuadorian-embassy |access-date=2019-04-06 |work=The Guardian |date=2019-04-05 |archive-date=2022-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220621090237/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2019/apr/05/why-is-wikileaks-founder-julian-assange-in-london-ecuadorian-embassy }}</ref>。阿桑奇父亲认为撤销庇护与[[国际货币基金组织|国际货币基金组织]]即将决定向厄瓜多尔发出一笔贷款有关<ref>{{cite news |last1=Booth |first1=William |last2=Adam |first2=Karla |title=WikiLeaks' Julian Assange sentenced to 50 weeks prison for jumping bail |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/wikileaks-julian-assange-sentenced-to-50-weeks-prison-in-bail-jumping-case/2019/05/01/d83c0190-6b6c-11e9-bbe7-1c798fb80536_story.html |access-date=2020-09-02 |newspaper=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] |url-access=subscription |archive-date=2021-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210924075730/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/wikileaks-julian-assange-sentenced-to-50-weeks-prison-in-bail-jumping-case/2019/05/01/d83c0190-6b6c-11e9-bbe7-1c798fb80536_story.html }}</ref>，而这个说法也是莫雷诺的反对者主张的，包括前外交部长{{tsl|en|Guillaume Long|纪尧姆·朗}}<ref name="itt140519">{{cite web |last1=Gibbons |first1=Chip |title=The Crackdown on Chelsea Manning and Julian Assange Is About Protecting U.S. Empire |url=https://inthesetimes.com/article/chelsea-manning-julian-assange-war-crimes-wikileaks-press-freedoms |website=In These Times |access-date=2020-09-02 |language=en |date=2019-05-14 |archive-date=2022-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220623035339/https://inthesetimes.com/article/chelsea-manning-julian-assange-war-crimes-wikileaks-press-freedoms }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Ecuadorian President's Motives for Surrendering Assange: Vengeance & IMF Loan? |url=https://therealnews.com/stories/ecuadorian-presidents-motives-for-surrendering-assange-vengeance-imf-loan |access-date=2020-09-02 |work=The Real News Network |date=2019-04-12 |archive-date=2020-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200908133257/https://therealnews.com/stories/ecuadorian-presidents-motives-for-surrendering-assange-vengeance-imf-loan }}</ref>。

2019年4月11日，厄瓜多尔政府邀请[[伦敦警察厅|伦敦警察厅]]按照美国引渡令进入大使馆逮捕阿桑奇<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.cnn.com/2019/04/11/uk/julian-assange-arrested-gbr-intl/index.html |title=Police arrest Julian Assange at Ecuadorian Embassy in London |publisher=CNN |date=2019-04-11 |access-date=2019-04-11 |archive-date=2022-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220409063624/https://www.cnn.com/2019/04/11/uk/julian-assange-arrested-gbr-intl/index.html }}</ref>。莫雷诺表示阿桑奇干涉厄瓜多尔内政，逾越了厄瓜多尔的容忍底线<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-47891737 |title=Wikileaks co-founder Julian Assange arrested |date=2019-04-11 |access-date=2019-04-11 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903184419/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-47891737 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Ecuador's president alleges Assange used London embassy as a 'center for spying' |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2019/04/15/ecuadors-president-alleges-assange-used-london-embassy-center-spying/ |first=Kayla |last=Epstein |access-date=2019-04-16 |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=2019-04-15 |url-access=subscription |archive-date=2020-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527075702/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2019/04/15/ecuadors-president-alleges-assange-used-london-embassy-center-spying/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Why Ecuador evicted 'spoiled brat' Assange from embassy |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/why-ecuador-ended-asylum-spoiled-brat-julian-assange-n993711 |publisher=[[NBC新聞|NBC News]] |access-date=2019-04-12 |archive-date=2022-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220621090054/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/why-ecuador-ended-asylum-spoiled-brat-julian-assange-n993711 }}</ref>。英国外交大臣[[杰里米·亨特|杰里米·亨特]]与首相[[文翠珊|文翠珊]]感谢莫雷诺配合行动<ref name="assangereactions">{{cite news |title=Julian Assange's arrest draws fierce international reaction |url=https://www.foxnews.com/world/wikileaks-julian-assange-arrest-international-reaction |publisher=Fox News Channel |date=2019-04-11 |accessdate=2022-06-18 |archive-date=2019-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413222042/https://www.foxnews.com/world/wikileaks-julian-assange-arrest-international-reaction }}</ref>。澳大利亚首相[[斯科特·莫里森|斯科特·莫里森]]表示有关行动与澳方无关，“完全是美国的事情”<ref>{{cite news |title=PM says no special treatment for Assange as his legal team vows to fight extradition |url=https://www.sbs.com.au/news/pm-says-no-special-treatment-for-assange-as-his-legal-team-vows-to-fight-extradition |work=SBS News |date=2019-04-11 |accessdate=2022-06-18 |archive-date=2021-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210726201407/https://www.sbs.com.au/news/pm-says-no-special-treatment-for-assange-as-his-legal-team-vows-to-fight-extradition }}</ref>。联合国特别报告员{{tsl|en|Agnès Callamard|阿涅斯·卡拉马尔}}认为英国当局肆意逮捕阿桑奇，有关行为威胁到生命安全<ref name="un_news_callamard_11_apr_2019">{{cite news |title=UN experts warn Assange arrest exposes him to risk of serious human rights violations |url=https://news.un.org/en/story/2019/04/1036491 |date=2019-04-11 |access-date=2021-09-25 |work=UN News |publisher=United Nations |archive-date=2022-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220621090054/https://news.un.org/en/story/2019/04/1036491 }}</ref>。

=== 在英國入獄 ===
